title: Vienna Teng - Inland Territory (2009) [VIPER666]
description:
Teng's musical style incorporates folk, pop, classical piano, and a cappella influences. She uses piano as her primary instrument and charges her lyrics with emotion, narrative, and personal history. Teng is a baseline alto but sings over a wide range.

Inland Territory is the fourth studio album by singer-songwriter Vienna Teng. It was released in Germany on February 6, 2009, and is scheduled to be released in the U.S. on April 7, 2009.[1] The record was recorded over five months in four cities.
